  "notes": "Sprint 127 - VS Code Extension Auto-Detect Project (SPEC-0015). Extension complete. Implements auto-detection of SDLC project from VS Code workspace folder, eliminating manual UUID configuration. Features: (1) ProjectDetector service scans workspace for .sdlc-config.json, (2) Auto-load project on extension activation, (3) ProjectsView UI updated to show auto-detected project. Reduces setup from 6 manual steps to 0. Workflow: User opens folder -> Extension auto-detects -> Project context loaded."
